dismissalText.commentary: Tanzid Hasan c Rahul b Patel 25 (25b 4x4 0x6 42m) SR: 100

dismissalComment.html: nicked off? KL Rahul is convinced. Axar isn't sure, and there's a longish delay before Paul Reiffel nods his head and puts his finger up! Tanzid is now trying to review, seemingly, but has run out of time. Replays show that is just as well, because it is a clear edge. Angled across him. Tanzid looks to punch through the off side, but is deceived by the lack of turn and gets an edge low on the bat through to Rahul, who takes a sharp chance
